text:
After a night of spiritual
reading with her hunky guru,

Samantha began to feel things she
hadn’t felt in a very long time:

She decided it was time
to put an end to her suffering.

But just as she reached the place
Krishna once called the gateway to life,

she turned back and
decided not to enter.
After all, she’d come this far.

She could continue
not to come at all.
